node.title: One dead after car crash near Queenstown
node.description: One person has died and another has been critically injured in a crash near Queenstown.
node.content:
["One person has died and another has been critically injured in a crash near Queenstown.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "Police say they were advised of the crash involving two cars on Kinsgton Road, Jacks Point at 6.10pm.", "Emergency services were at the scene and traffic management was in place."]
